---
import svgPinkStar from '../assets/pink-star.svg'
import Button from './Button.astro'
---

<section class="px-3" id="contact">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto bg-white text-center flex flex-col gap-4 border-3 shadow-[8px_8px_0px_rgba(0,0,0,0.3)] relative p-10">
      <h1 class="text-3xl">If the work resonates, let's talk.</h1>
      <p class="text-lg max-w-lg mx-auto">I'm selective about where I take my skills next, and I imagine you're selective too.</p>
      <p class="text-lg max-w-lg mx-auto">If you're building something that needs sharp positioning, a GTM motion that actually converts, or an enablement system that gives sales what they need to close, I'd like to hear about it.</p>
      <div class="flex justify-center gap-4 flex-wrap">
        <Button text="Get in touch →" link="mailto:aslialimesimsek@gmail.com" target="_self" />
        <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/aslialimesimsek" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="flex items-center gap-1 underline underline-offset-4 text-sm">Connect on LinkedIn</a>
      </div>
      <img src={svgPinkStar.src} alt="svg" width="80" class="absolute -top-10 right-20" />
    </div>
</section>
